Rawlings Glove Builder, This extension gives facility to bulid custome glove and add order of the custome glove. There are two types of leathers Pro Preferred and Heart of the Hide. There are lots of option to build custome glove like leather colour and etc.Need to create two products with SKU HOHCG,PROPRFCG coressponding leathers Pro Preferred and Heart of the Hide and also set price of these products.



Features of Rawlings Glove Builder Module

- Create an interface to set Rawlings Glove Builder credential.
- Lots of oprion to make custome glove 

